        {
            "id": 6011046,
            "title": "週三、週五「雙到期日」起跑！臺指選擇權週五到期契約自6/27掛牌上市",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>臺灣期貨交易所（期交所）將於 6 月 27 日推出「週五到期臺指選擇權」，首個契約到期日 7 月 11 日（週五）。期交所表示，繼現行週三到期週契約後，新增週間另一主要到期日，建立每星期有「週三」及「週五」2 個到期日的全新架構，將可提升市場對短天期避險及事件交易的彈性與效率。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011046%2Fl%2F6a476da98617a7d38f584638d56ff611.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">週三、週五「雙到期日」起跑！臺指選擇權週五到期契約自6/27掛牌上市。（鉅亨網資料照）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新契約每週五掛牌，初次上市日為 6 月 27 日（週五），首個契約到期日為 2 週後的 7 月 11 日（週五）。除首週（即 7 月 4 日無契約到期）外，之後每週五均有週契約到期。其履約價格間距、序列等契約規格皆與現行週三到期週契約相同。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>因應全球多項重要經濟數據及企業財報常於週四晚間發布，週五到期契約可協助交易人於週四日盤預先布局，週四夜盤因應實際數據或財報結果即時調整部位，或於週五結算、避免週末風險，精準對應事件發生時點、即時反應市場波動、當週內完成避險或獲利了結，且存續期間短、權利金較低的特性，也大幅提高資金運用效率。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>期交所指出，週三及週五雙到期日架構，更可多元化交易與避險策略。例如觀察週三、週五到期契約的隱含波動率，進行波動率交易；或利用不同到期日之時間價值消逝速度差異，進行時間價差交易；或同時持有不同到期日部位，降低集中到期風險，避免因市場突然大幅波動導致單一到期日部位受損。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>週五到期臺指選擇權的推出，賦予交易人更大彈性，並針對重大市場事件進行精準的策略部署。同時，透過完整的週三與週五密集的到期架構，更能精確反映市場對不同時間點的預期和波動率看法，發揮價格發現功能，增強市場深度與活絡度，為臺灣期貨市場注入全新成長動能。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
